column5: no more crowds and clusters for me before   and the after     and not another person in sight

Funny we were just talkin bout Calendonia the other day---Ya know when I was a kid--that weir in the picture was not there and I used to sit and  fish on the bottom pads of that railway tressle in the holes around them--need scuba gear now.  Cool Pic  Bushart
i don't like fishing elbow to elbow either....
So have you moved out east Pure, or have you taken to fishing in peoples wishing wells? Jim
lol some of them prob are wishing wells but yes im out east now
Well fill us in man. Where are you? Have you found work? Is there a Timmy's near by? You have become a man of few words. Jim

yah i have work starting on thurs, the closet timmys is about 20 min away....  but the local bar isnt to far im living on my grandparents farm and you can spin your self around and walk and find a stream filled with trout in 10min, its a bit of a change but i might stay for a while atlantic salmon run a river around the corner  :)
Sounds like a great place Pure, nice pictures on top also.  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
